In the report, which evaluates 144 countries, the UAE has presented 78 economic, social and economic indicators in just one year.

The UAE is the world's first in the lack of inflation and the absence of organized crime and the second in the effectiveness of government spending and the third globally in confidence in the leadership and government
The UAE is also the world's first in road quality, second globally in aviation infrastructure and third in the world in the lack of government bureaucracy

Azerbaijani team won 10 medals at the II Summer Olympic Games among juniors in Nanjing, China and gained 12 medals
Five of them are gold medals and 6th among European countries and the first among Muslim countries.
Taking into account that more than 200 teams participated in the Summer Olympic Games, this is a great and historic victory.
Azerbaijan is a sporting country, said the leaders of the International Olympic Movement.
National Olympic Committee of Azerbaijan, Ministry of Youth and Sport, federations, sports societies, clubs (cont) http://t.co/LQUCjdZ621
Today Azerbaijan is developing thoroughly and development of sports, of course, reflects the overall development of our country.
The sporting policy of the Azerbaijani state opens great opportunities for every youth.
European Games will be held for the first time next year.
The holding of these games has been entrusted to Azerbaijan. It is a great responsibility and a great achievement of Azerbaijani sports.
The European Games will allow Azerbaijan to present itself to all Europe as a strong, developing and modern state.
Our athletes are at the top of the games, both intellectually and physically.
You are young, you were born during the years of independence and your victories are the power of the Azerbaijani state.
The young, independent Azerbaijan state is capable of achieving great successes, it will do and will do.
A country like ours will not be cowed by barbaric killers. We have faced down threats like this before and we will do so again.
